19:42.735 --> 19:43.668
I can't believe people think I'm gay.

19:43.703 --> 19:46.772
Oh, come on, laugh it
off. It's ridiculous.

19:46.806 --> 19:49.574
You're not gay just because
your mother is gay. I'm not gay.

19:49.609 --> 19:51.409
No one thinks you're gay. That's
why you can laugh about it.

19:51.444 --> 19:52.778
