20:57.491 --> 21:00.293
By the way, I got all my
stuff out of Ashley's room.

21:00.327 --> 21:01.594
You didn't have to do that.
She'll be out of here in a week.

21:01.628 --> 21:04.297
You can keep the room. Yeah, we'll see.

21:04.331 --> 21:06.632
