23:08.455 --> 23:11.524
I just thought I'd stop by, say hello.

23:11.558 --> 23:12.558
Wait for Ashley to get home?

23:12.592 --> 23:14.460
Ashley's coming home? Tonight?

23:14.494 --> 23:16.529
