mentioned that I am Ricky's mom

23:35.515 --> 23:40.386
and I'm going to be Amy's
mother-in-law, because Amy is not gay.

23:40.420 --> 23:41.320
So it's just Anne?

23:41.355 --> 23:44.423
How did you know about that?

23:44.458 --> 23:48.561
I'll tell you how, because some bigmouth
said something about it to someone

23:48.595 --> 23:53.366
