24:08.281 --> 24:09.482
What point?

24:09.516 --> 24:10.483
Oh, you've been hit, too.

24:10.517 --> 24:12.485
Hit?

24:12.519 --> 24:13.386
By the rumors.

24:13.420 --> 24:17.323
Oh, I can't wait.
What is it? What is it?

24:17.357 --> 24:20.493
Oh, you'll like this.
Apparently, you turn women gay.

24:20.527 --> 24:23.195
No, I don't!

24:23.230 --> 24:25.331
Oh! (LAUGHS)

24:25.365 --> 24:26.532
