24:26.566 --> 24:28.434
You are or you aren't
or you're figuring it out

24:28.468 --> 24:30.369
or emerging or evolving or whatever.

24:30.404 --> 24:32.405
You've been reading again, haven't you?

24:32.439 --> 24:33.539
