24:52.325 --> 24:53.392
(SIGHS) I wish I had.

24:53.427 --> 24:53.759
Well, it's not too late.

24:53.794 --> 24:55.594
No, it is.

24:55.629 --> 24:57.363
Are you okay?

24:57.397 --> 24:59.532
Mom, do we have any...

25:01.201 --> 25:02.535
