25:46.513 --> 25:49.315
if we are off the hook,

25:49.349 --> 25:51.283
the two of us, you and me.

25:51.318 --> 25:52.384
For what?

25:52.419 --> 25:54.587
He's the one who opened
his big mouth and told us

25:54.621 --> 25:56.255
