get along with Anne.

26:03.497 --> 26:04.530
Well, you don't have to
get along with her too well.

26:04.564 --> 26:08.167
What? What do you mean?

26:08.201 --> 26:10.302
You don't have to sleep with her.

26:10.337 --> 26:11.403
