28:03.350 --> 28:03.682
Sorry.

28:03.717 --> 28:05.484
No problem.

28:10.290 --> 28:11.457
I can't believe I said that.

28:11.491 --> 28:13.325
Forget about it. It
didn't mean anything.

28:13.360 --> 28:14.426
I know, but still... Hey.

28:14.461 --> 28:16.195
I said I've thought
about kissing a girl.

28:16.229 --> 28:18.497
Doesn't make me gay.

28:18.531 --> 28:20.232
